extends com.liferay.portal.model.BaseModel<AHAddr>
    The base model interface for the AHAddr service. Represents a row in the "AHADDR" database table, with each column mapped to a property of this class.

    This interface and its corresponding implementation de.fraunhofer.fokus.oefit.particity.model.impl.AHAddrModelImpl exist only as a container for the default property accessors generated by ServiceBuilder. Helper methods and all application logic should be put in de.fraunhofer.fokus.oefit.particity.model.impl.AHAddrImpl.
